data.description: Grab your vision and RUN to this amazing jewel right in the middle of town.  Tucked away on a cul-de-sac street in the hot Underwood Hills neighborhood in West Midtown, this cottage oozes potential, charm and a magical backyard.  The three bedrooms and two bathrooms are rock solid, just vault the large living / dining room area, paint the kitchen and enjoy!  If you get really ambitious, vault the living area and open up the wall into the light-filled kitchen.  There's a full apartment on the terrance level, so live in it while renovating the main level, then use the apartment as an income source when everything is done upstairs.  Large workroom and storage room to keep all the supplies while you're renovating.  When the work is done, enjoy that amazing backyard with the multiple decks, Koi pond (the Koi can stay!), the stone path through the pollinator garden and the level backyard beyond that.  See this today, it won't last.
